dcterms:description: The SHHS dataset is a collection of data from different centers that studies how breathing problems during sleep affect heart diseases. It includes PSG recordings with manual annotations for sleep stages and arousal events.
dcterms:title: Sleep Heart Health Study (SHHS)

dcterms:description: The MESA study investigates factors associated with subclinical cardiovascular disease and includes PSG recordings with annotations for sleep stages and arousal events.
